duler Design\n   584\t\n   585\t`run_scheduler.sh` runs `live_runner.js` every 1
0 minutes. The container replaces it:\n   586\t\n   587\t```dockerfile\n   588\t
CMD ["sh", "-c", "while true; do node strategies/live_runner.js; sleep 600; done
