mations \\\n   607\t    metricName=PipelineFailures,metricNamespace=Tokenfly,met
ricValue=1\n   608\t```\n   609\t\n   610\t### CloudWatch Alarm — Alert on Failu
re\n   611\t\n   612\t```bash\n   613\taws cloudwatch put-metric-alarm \\\n   61
4\t  --alarm-name tokenfly-pipeline-failure \\\n   615\t  --metric-name Pipeline
Failures \\\n   616\t  --namespace Tokenfly \\\n   617\t  --statistic Sum \\\n  
618\t  --period 600 \\\n   619\t  --threshold 1 \\\n   620\t  --comparison-opera
tor GreaterThanOrEqualToThreshold \\\n   621\t  --evaluation-periods 1 \\\n   62
2\t  --alarm-actions arn:aws:sns:us-east-1:ACCOUNT:tokenfly-alerts\n   623\t```\
n   624\t\n   625\t### Key metrics to watch\n   626\t| Metric | Threshold | Acti
on |\n   627\t|--------|-----------|--------|\n   628\t| Pipeline FAILED in logs
| Any occurrence | Page via SNS |\n   629\t| EC2 CPUUtilization | > 80% for 5 mi
