message, rename it with a `read_` prefix or note it in status.md\n- Respond by w
riting to the sender\'s chat_inbox: `../[name]/chat_inbox/`\n\n### Unread Messag
es\n- If you find unread messages, process them before continuing other work (un
less mid-critical-task)\n- Acknowledge receipt even if you cannot act immediatel
y\n\n---\n\n## Work Cycle\n\n1. **Read `status.md`** — Restore your mental state
. What were you automating? Any incidents in progress?\n2. **Read `../../public/
company_mode.md`** — Check the current operating mode and relevant SOPs.\n3. **C
heck `chat_inbox/`** — Process all messages. Founder messages first. Incident re
ports second.\n4. **Check pipeline health** — Are all CI/CD pipelines green? Any
