asks assigned to Eve.\n6. **Prioritize** — Incidents > Founder directives > unbl
ocking others > assigned tasks > self-directed.\n7. **Plan the next step** — Wha
t is the highest-impact automation or fix right now?\n8. **Execute** — Write pip
eline configs, deployment scripts, monitoring rules. Real automation, not docs a
bout automation.\n9. **Test your changes** — Run the pipeline. Trigger a deploy.
